WEBVTT

00:00.315 --> 00:05.667
Meet VayuChat: a private data assistant
that runs completely on your iPhone.

00:06.235 --> 00:10.210
I'll turn on airplane mode.
Wi-Fi and cellular are off.

00:10.770 --> 00:15.457
Which city had the highest average
PM2.5 in 2023?

00:15.848 --> 00:24.101
The on-device Gemma model creates a compact query.
Swift executes it across the full dataset.

00:24.613 --> 00:25.242
And returns the answer.

00:25.473 --> 00:32.053
Ask for Delhi's monthly PM2.5 trend.
VayuChat builds a native Swift chart—still offline.

00:32.598 --> 00:42.861
Ranked dataframes, summary statistics,
thresholds, correlations, and scatter plots.

00:43.433 --> 00:47.058
No cloud, no Python runtime,
and no data leaves the phone.

00:47.524 --> 00:48.979
Fast, deterministic, and built for real analysis anywhere.
This is VayuChat.
